Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開幕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我兒子就是不肯叫我老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還把老家給燒掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我兒子也一個人離家出走不回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家家有本難念的經啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 來塊油炸豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要魚肉山芋片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.09,0:00:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs130\pos(960,850)\fn方正舒体_GBK}來我家坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你其實很怕孤獨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.64,0:00:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家哪有這樣子~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs130\pos(960,850)\fn方正舒体_GBK}變身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來要動真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說這把武器我用得還不太熟練…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法變身~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,純真可愛☆布拉德雷~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs130\pos(960,850)\fn方正舒体_GBK}胡爺爺之死！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老夫命不久矣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少給蘭芳留下點什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咽氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fs130\pos(960,850)\fn方正舒体_GBK}巴卡尼亞之死！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利麟加入了我們這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下我死而無憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 我心裏再也沒有什麼遺…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去向作戰總部投降 快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝您 上尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 人生唯一一次桃花運錯過了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉！
